This is the simple Fetch Quest setup.

You can use any tag for any item that you want the PC to pick up, but make sure it's unique. If you have a specific item in mind that you need put into a different area, just let the Dev DMs know!

Make sure the resref of any item reward points to an item that's on the module's palette. If you need to make an entirely new item for it, remember to send that along in the .erf for the update also so it can be added. It should also be entirely unique to the quest so that it doesn't overwrite anything that already exists, so be careful about that.

This is the Multichain Quest setup which requires a specific order to the quest stops.

You can have as many or as few stops as you want, so have fun.
